ai.nuralogix.anurasdk.core

Interface ExposureOptimizerPipe

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, DfxPipeListener, Module, VideoPipe, VideoSource

    public interface ExposureOptimizerPipe
extends VideoPipe, DfxPipeListener
    This video pipe adjusts current image frame's brightness for the best measurement result.

    This pipe must be connected after DfxPipe
